ttn: Legal, DMCA complaints

I, the undersigned, CERTIFY UNDER PENALTY OF PERJURY that I am an agent

listed below are not authorized by the above IP Owner, its agent, or the
law and therefore infringe the IP Owner's rights according to state,
federal, or United States law. Please act expeditiously to remove or
disable access to the material or items claimed to be infringing.
